      "text": "For me assessing and warming up the horse go hand in hand. At the beginning of each and every training session with our horse we must stand back and make an assessment of what we have to work with. This assessment includes the way our horse looks and feels, and also very importantly, how we feel. ",
      "id": "1229672007764"
